image_analysis.description: This is a page from a financial disclosure form, specifically OGE Form 278e, filed by Donald J. Trump. The page, numbered 9 of 51, details positions he held in various organizations outside the United States Government. It is presented as a table listing the organization name, location, type, position held, and the start and end dates of the position.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header with form details and the filer's name. The main body consists of a multi-column table. A footer contains an explanatory note and a document identification number.
